OL,3,CWater industry faces 'root and branch
OL,4,Creform' after landmark review
OL,6,FThe water industry is set to be
OL,7,Fcompletely overhauled following the
OL,8,Fpublication of a landmark review of
OL,9,Fthe sector on Monday.
OL,11,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed is
OL,12,Fexpected to promise "root and branch
OL,13,Freform" of the sector in a bid to
OL,14,Fclean up England's rivers and limit
OL,15,Frises in water bills.
OL,17,FThe commitment will follow the
OL,18,Fpublication of the final report of the
OL,19,FIndependent Water Commission led by
OL,20,Fformer Bank of England deputy governor
OL,21,FSir Jon Cunliffe.
