OL,3,CWater industry faces 'root and branch
OL,4,Creform' after landmark review
OL,6,FIn a speech responding to Sir Jon's
OL,7,Freport, Mr Reed is set to describe the
OL,8,Fwater industry as "broken" and welcome
OL,9,Fthe commission's recommendations to
OL,10,Fensure "the failures of the past can
OL,11,Fnever happen again".
OL,13,FHe is also widely reported to be
OL,14,Fpreparing to abolish the industry's
OL,15,Fbeleaguered regulator Ofwat, which has
OL,16,Ffaced criticism for overseeing a sharp
OL,17,Frise in sewage pollution while failing
OL,18,Fto crack down on executive pay and
OL,19,Flarge dividends at debt-ridden water
OL,20,Fcompanies.
