OL,3,CWater industry faces 'root and branch
OL,4,Creform' after landmark review
OL,6,FIn his interim report, Sir Jon
OL,7,Fcriticised the way the sector was
OL,8,Fregulated, with duties split between
OL,9,FOfwat, the Environment Agency and the
OL,10,FDrinking Water Inspectorate.
OL,12,FOn Sunday, Mr Reed would not confirm
OL,13,Fthat Ofwat was in line to be scrapped,
OL,14,Fbut declined to express confidence in
OL,15,Fthe regulator either, saying it was
OL,16,F"clearly failing".
OL,18,FBoth the Conservatives and the Liberal
OL,19,FDemocrats have agreed that water
OL,20,Fregulation needs to change.
