OL,3,CWater industry faces 'root and branch
OL,4,Creform' after landmark review
OL,6,FUrging the Government to be
OL,7,F"transparent" about what would replace
OL,8,FOfwat and how it would work, Tory
OL,9,Fshadow environment secretary Victoria
OL,10,FAtkins said: "No one disputes that the
OL,11,Fwater sector is under pressure, and we
OL,12,Fall want to see meaningful
OL,13,Fimprovements.
OL,15,F"Reforming regulation must be focused
OL,16,Fon improving performance and
OL,17,Fguaranteeing water security."
