OL,3,CWater industry faces 'root and branch
OL,4,Creform' after landmark review
OL,6,FLib Dem leader Sir Ed Davey has called
OL,7,Ffor the creation of a Clean Water
OL,8,FAuthority that could "hold these water
OL,9,Fcompanies to account" and "fine them
OL,10,Fwhen they fail".
OL,12,FWhile Mr Reed has pledged to avoid the
OL,13,Fneed for "huge shock hikes" in water
OL,14,Fbills, such as the 26% increase seen
OL,15,Fthis year, reform is unlikely to lead
OL,16,Fto a fall in costs for consumers.
