OL,6,FThe Government hopes that investment
OL,7,Fin long-neglected infrastructure will
OL,8,Fmake large bill increases unnecessary,
OL,9,Fbut Mr Reed acknowledged on Sunday
OL,10,Fthat there needed to be "appropriate
OL,11,Fbill rises" to secure "appropriate
OL,12,Flevels of investment".
OL,14,FHe is also unlikely to commit to
OL,15,Fexpanding social tariffs that could
OL,16,Fhelp households struggling with bills
OL,17,Fat the cost of higher charges for
OL,18,Fwealthier families, saying he was yet
OL,19,Fto be convinced that this was needed.
