OL,3,CWater industry faces 'root and branch
OL,4,Creform' after landmark review
OL,6,FPrior to Monday's announcement, Mr
OL,7,FReed had already committed to halving
OL,8,Fsewage pollution in England's rivers
OL,9,Fby 2030 thanks to a #104 billion
OL,10,Finvestment from the sector in
OL,11,Fupgrading infrastructure.
OL,13,FHe has also announced the creation of
OL,14,Fa new, legally binding water
OL,15,Fombudsman, expanding the role of the
OL,16,Fvoluntary Consumer Council for Water
OL,17,Fand bringing the sector into line with
OL,18,Fother utilities.
