OL,6,FBut the Conservatives have accused
OL,7,FLabour of copying the policies of the
OL,8,Fprevious government.
OL,10,FMs Atkins said: "Labour have already
OL,11,Fwasted a year since the general
OL,12,Felection as they came into office with
OL,13,Fno plans for water, instead claiming
OL,14,Fthat the work we started in office is
OL,15,Ftheir own."
